rch are empty o you clevers\nFields of writing books are empty o you clevers\nFields of crops and harvesting are empty o you clevers\nFields of work and building are empty o you clevers\nFields of integrity and ethics are empty o you clevers\nFields of solidarity and brotherly helping are empty o you clevers\nI wonder why fields of my country are empty o you clevers\n \nWritten By Ahmed A Jadallah\n8/31/2010","creator_id":1,"presentationStyle":1}